ieee8021TpmrMib.description: Two-Port MAC Relay (TPMR) MIB module. Unless otherwise indicated, the references in this MIB module are to IEEE 802.1Q-2011. Copyright(c) IEEE This MIB module is part of IEEE Std. 802.1aj; please refer to the document itself for full legal notices.

IEEE8021TpmrFrameDiscardErrorReason.name: IEEE8021TpmrFrameDiscardErrorReason
IEEE8021TpmrFrameDiscardErrorReason.description: A reason code for a frame discard error.

ieee8021TpmrPortTable.name: ieee8021TpmrPortTable
ieee8021TpmrPortTable.description: The TPMR port table. Each row in the table represents a TPMR port. By definition there are two ports per TPMR. Note that the indices of this table are equivalent to those of the ieee8021BridgeBasePortTable in the IEEE8021-BRIDGE-MIB, with ieee8021TpmrPortNumber having a more limited value range than ieee8021BridgeBasePort.

ieee8021TpmrPortNumber.name: ieee8021TpmrPortNumber
ieee8021TpmrPortNumber.description: The number of this TPMR port.

ieee8021TpmrPortMgmtAddr.name: ieee8021TpmrPortMgmtAddr
ieee8021TpmrPortMgmtAddr.description: Is 'true' if the TPMR port MAC address is the management address of the TPMR, otheriwse 'false'.

ieee8021TpmrPortMgmtAddrForwarding.name: ieee8021TpmrPortMgmtAddrForwarding
ieee8021TpmrPortMgmtAddrForwarding.description: Is 'true' if forwarding is enabled for frames destined to the management address of the TPMR, otherwise 'false'.

ieee8021TpmrPortStatsTable.name: ieee8021TpmrPortStatsTable
ieee8021TpmrPortStatsTable.description: The TPMR port statistics table. Each row in the table represents a TPMR port. By definition there are two ports per TPMR. Discontinuities in the value of counters in this table can occur at re-initialization of the management system, and at other times as indicated by the value of IF-MIB ifCounterDiscontinuityTime.

ieee8021TpmrPortStatsEntry.name: ieee8021TpmrPortStatsEntry
ieee8021TpmrPortStatsEntry.description: A TPMR port counters table entry.

ieee8021TpmrPortStatsRxFrames.name: ieee8021TpmrPortStatsRxFrames
ieee8021TpmrPortStatsRxFrames.description: Count of all valid frames received on this port (including BPDUs, frames addressed to the TPMR as an end station, and frames that were submitted to the Forwarding Process).

ieee8021TpmrPortStatsRxOctets.name: ieee8021TpmrPortStatsRxOctets
ieee8021TpmrPortStatsRxOctets.description: Count of the total number of octets in all valid frames received on this port (including BPDUs, frames addressed to the TPMR as an end station, and frames that were submitted to the Forwarding Process).

ieee8021TpmrPortStatsFramesForwarded.name: ieee8021TpmrPortStatsFramesForwarded
ieee8021TpmrPortStatsFramesForwarded.description: Count of all frames that were received on this port and were forwarded to the transmission port.

ieee8021TpmrPortStatsFramesDiscarded.name: ieee8021TpmrPortStatsFramesDiscarded
ieee8021TpmrPortStatsFramesDiscarded.description: Count of all frames that were received on this port but were discarded by the Forwarding Process for any reason.

ieee8021TpmrPortStatsFramesDiscardedQueu.name: ieee8021TpmrPortStatsFramesDiscardedQueueFull
ieee8021TpmrPortStatsFramesDiscardedQueu.description: Count of all frames received on this port that were to be transmitted through the transmission port but were discarded due to lack of available queue space.

ieee8021TpmrPortStatsFramesDiscardedLife.name: ieee8021TpmrPortStatsFramesDiscardedLifetime
ieee8021TpmrPortStatsFramesDiscardedLife.description: Count of all frames received on this port that were to be transmitted through the transmission port but were discarded due to their frame lifetime having been exceeded.

ieee8021TpmrPortStatsFramesDiscardedErro.name: ieee8021TpmrPortStatsFramesDiscardedError
ieee8021TpmrPortStatsFramesDiscardedErro.description: Count of all frames received on this port that were to be transmitted through the transmission port but could not be transmitted (e.g., frame too large).

ieee8021TpmrPortDiscardDetailsTable.name: ieee8021TpmrPortDiscardDetailsTable
ieee8021TpmrPortDiscardDetailsTable.description: The TPMR frames discard details table. Each row in the table represents a discarded frame on a TPMR port. By definition there are two ports per TPMR. This table is maintained as a FIFO. A new entry is inserted in the first row, and existing entries are shuffled down, with the last entry being discarded. Because of the FIFO behaviour, the relationship between the index and contents will change when an entry is added to the table. This may result in apparent duplication of row content during a table traversal.

ieee8021TpmrPortDiscardDetailsEntry.name: ieee8021TpmrPortDiscardDetailsEntry
ieee8021TpmrPortDiscardDetailsEntry.description: A TPMR frames discarded error details table entry.

ieee8021TpmrPortDiscardDetailsIndex.name: ieee8021TpmrPortDiscardDetailsIndex
ieee8021TpmrPortDiscardDetailsIndex.description: The second index of a TPMR frames discard details table entry.

ieee8021TpmrPortDiscardDetailsSource.name: ieee8021TpmrPortDiscardDetailsSource
ieee8021TpmrPortDiscardDetailsSource.description: The source MAC address of the discarded frame.

ieee8021TpmrPortDiscardDetailsReason.name: ieee8021TpmrPortDiscardDetailsReason
ieee8021TpmrPortDiscardDetailsReason.description: The reason why the frame was discarded.

ieee8021TpmrMspTable.name: ieee8021TpmrMspTable
ieee8021TpmrMspTable.description: The TPMR MAC status propagation performance table. Each row in the table represents a TPMR port. By definition there are two ports per TPMR. The persistence of writable objects in a conceptual row of this table is determined by the value of the ieee8021TpmrMspStorageType object.

ieee8021TpmrMspEntry.name: ieee8021TpmrMspEntry
ieee8021TpmrMspEntry.description: A TPMR MAC status propagation performance table entry.

ieee8021TpmrMspLinkNotify.name: ieee8021TpmrMspLinkNotify
ieee8021TpmrMspLinkNotify.description: The value of LinkNotify used by the MSP state machines.

ieee8021TpmrMspLinkNotifyWait.name: ieee8021TpmrMspLinkNotifyWait
ieee8021TpmrMspLinkNotifyWait.description: The value of LinkNotifyWait used by the MSP state machines.

ieee8021TpmrMspLinkNotifyRetry.name: ieee8021TpmrMspLinkNotifyRetry
ieee8021TpmrMspLinkNotifyRetry.description: The value of LinkNotifyRetry used by the MSP state machines.

ieee8021TpmrMspMacNotify.name: ieee8021TpmrMspMacNotify
ieee8021TpmrMspMacNotify.description: The value of MacNotify used by the MSP state machines.

ieee8021TpmrMspMacNotifyTime.name: ieee8021TpmrMspMacNotifyTime
ieee8021TpmrMspMacNotifyTime.description: The value of MacNotifyTime used by the MSP state machines.

ieee8021TpmrMspMacRecoverTime.name: ieee8021TpmrMspMacRecoverTime
ieee8021TpmrMspMacRecoverTime.description: The value of MacRecoverTime used by the MSP state machines.

ieee8021TpmrMspStorageType.name: ieee8021TpmrMspStorageType
ieee8021TpmrMspStorageType.description: The storage type for all read-write objects within this row. Conceptual rows having the value 'permanent' need not allow write access to any columnar objects in the row. If this object has the value 'volatile', modifications to read-write objects in this row are not persistent across reboots or restarts. If this object has the value 'nonVolatile', modifications to objects in this row are persistent.

ieee8021TpmrMspStatsTable.name: ieee8021TpmrMspStatsTable
ieee8021TpmrMspStatsTable.description: The TPMR MAC status propagation statistics table. Each row in the table represents a TPMR port. By definition there are two ports per TPMR. Discontinuities in the value of counters in this table can occur at re-initialization of the management system, and at other times as indicated by the value of IF-MIB ifCounterDiscontinuityTime.

ieee8021TpmrMspStatsEntry.name: ieee8021TpmrMspStatsEntry
ieee8021TpmrMspStatsEntry.description: A TPMR MAC status propagation statistics table entry.

ieee8021TpmrMspStatsTxAcks.name: ieee8021TpmrMspStatsTxAcks
ieee8021TpmrMspStatsTxAcks.description: The number of acks transmitted by the port's Transmit Process as a consequence of txAck being set.

ieee8021TpmrMspStatsTxAddNotifications.name: ieee8021TpmrMspStatsTxAddNotifications
ieee8021TpmrMspStatsTxAddNotifications.description: The number of adds transmitted by the port's Transmit Process as a consequence of txAdd being set.

ieee8021TpmrMspStatsTxAddConfirmations.name: ieee8021TpmrMspStatsTxAddConfirmations
ieee8021TpmrMspStatsTxAddConfirmations.description: The number of add confirms transmitted by the port's Transmit Process as a consequence of txAddConfirm being set.

ieee8021TpmrMspStatsTxLossNotifications.name: ieee8021TpmrMspStatsTxLossNotifications
ieee8021TpmrMspStatsTxLossNotifications.description: The number of losses transmitted by the port's Transmit Process as a consequence of txLoss being set.

ieee8021TpmrMspStatsTxLossConfirmations.name: ieee8021TpmrMspStatsTxLossConfirmations
ieee8021TpmrMspStatsTxLossConfirmations.description: The number of loss confirms transmitted by the port's Transmit Process as a consequence of txLossConfirm being set.

ieee8021TpmrMspStatsRxAcks.name: ieee8021TpmrMspStatsRxAcks
ieee8021TpmrMspStatsRxAcks.description: The number of acks received by the port's Receive Process.

ieee8021TpmrMspStatsRxAddNotifications.name: ieee8021TpmrMspStatsRxAddNotifications
ieee8021TpmrMspStatsRxAddNotifications.description: The number of adds received by the port's Receive Process.

ieee8021TpmrMspStatsRxAddConfirmations.name: ieee8021TpmrMspStatsRxAddConfirmations
ieee8021TpmrMspStatsRxAddConfirmations.description: The number of add confirms received by the port's Receive Process.

ieee8021TpmrMspStatsRxLossNotifications.name: ieee8021TpmrMspStatsRxLossNotifications
ieee8021TpmrMspStatsRxLossNotifications.description: The number of losses received by the port's Receive Process.

ieee8021TpmrMspStatsRxLossConfirmations.name: ieee8021TpmrMspStatsRxLossConfirmations
ieee8021TpmrMspStatsRxLossConfirmations.description: The number of loss confirms received by the port's Receive Process.

ieee8021TpmrMspStatsAddEvents.name: ieee8021TpmrMspStatsAddEvents
ieee8021TpmrMspStatsAddEvents.description: The number of transitions to STM:ADD directly from STM:DOWN or STM:LOSS.

ieee8021TpmrMspStatsLossEvents.name: ieee8021TpmrMspStatsLossEvents
ieee8021TpmrMspStatsLossEvents.description: The number of transitions to STM:LOSS directly from STM:UP or STM:ADD.

ieee8021TpmrMspStatsMacStatusNotificatio.name: ieee8021TpmrMspStatsMacStatusNotifications
ieee8021TpmrMspStatsMacStatusNotificatio.description: The number of transitions to SNM:MAC_NOTIFICATION.

ieee8021TpmrCompliance.name: ieee8021TpmrCompliance
ieee8021TpmrCompliance.description: The compliance statement for device support of TPMR.
